name: Pigs Dinner - print
description:
A limited edition digital print of my artwork Pigs Dinner, one of my favourite collage style prints on wood. Looking at the way we consume in excess, hungry for more. The title was inspired by an early short horror story I read when I was 15 years old.
Edition of 10 - print 30 x 42 cm

name: Action Girl - print
description:
A limited edition print of one my top selling shirt designs. Action girl delivers the goods with an inverted look into the secret night life of a sexy Nikita doing her thing.
Digital print edition of 10, 30 x 42 cm.

name: Bris Best Fest
description: A celebration of street art and hip hop culture, featuring the Son of Sam range in all it's urban ambiguity.

name: Son of Sam
description:
The iconic image of yours truly posterised in goodness. This image was taken a few years ago when I was growing my moustache for movember. I thought I looked like a revolutionary, but one of my teachers said I looked like a back-packer murderer. I'll let you decide.
Limited edition digital print of 10, 30 x 42 cm.

name: Soul Music
description:
Limited edition digital print.
This is a photograph of one of my favourite sculptures "Soul Music". I have then reduced the image to one layer, incorporating the brickwork in the background. Soul music was made from ceramic, creating a life-like skull and skeletal arm. With the torso being an old speaker box I found on the side of the road.
Limited edition of 10, digital print is 30 x 42cm.

name: Winter Launch
description: I'm launching the winter range of clothing at JamJar in West End. Also exhibiting my artwork on the walls, as well as some sexy people modelling my new threads. Shall be a fun night.

name: Contraband Exhibition
description: Great show to be apart of, exhibited with some really good artists and had a fantastic time.

name: Finders Keepers Boutique Market
description:
The ever eclectic Finders Keepers designer market is back. I'll be launching some new designs along with some nice fruity, spring summery colours. So if you're in Brisbane come down to the Old Museum and check it out.

http://www.thefinderskeepers.com/son-of-sam.php

name: Finders Keepers Melbourne
description: Hey Melbourne peeps and perps, come check out the latest designs and creations this country has to offer. Located at the Royal exhibition building in Carlton, this boutique designer market always follows through.

name: Face of Sam
description:
This is a photograph of one of my screen prints on wood. The image is an inverted picture of my face printed with a layer of blue paint, then a layer of red over the top. I like the raw aspect of this image, with a dark and mysterious undertone.
Limited edition of 10 digital prints, 30 x 42 cm.

name: Summer Launch
description: Launching the summer range in style. Was a night with great people, art, fashion, and fantastic beats by DJ Tigermoth.

name: GoMa & GoPa
description: Recent exhibition of contemporary sculpture, painting, printmaking and street art. Featuring artists Sam Butel, Anthony Jigalin, Guido Van Helten, Barek, LUCKS and ZKLR.
